phrases: In this year, which would later come be known as the first year of the Third Galactic Empire,
humanity was in the midst of expanding its sphere of activity beyond Earth.
The development of Dyson Spheres accelerated humanity's progress into space,
and 70 of the total population now resides in space.
This is JIOR Sphere No. 1, Module 77.
Please transmit your country of registration
You are carrying two transfer students for Sakimori Academy, is that correct?
This is still neck and neck!
We are on the home stretch!
It is apparently an eating contest to decide who gets to use the school field.
I cannot believe high schoolers would still be fighting over who gets to use the track...
We were counting on you, man...
I told you I did not want to do it...
We rock-paper-scissored for it, and you lost.
The odds of the loser winning the next time are
Haruto has absolutely no head for competitions.
Someone in a weird shirt like that has no room to talk.
The weather in the module is fair today, and Hm?
Your manifest said that there were two transfer students.
Peace has made this JIOR country soft.
In short, this was settled by the balance of power between the countries of Dorssia and ARUS.
The defining characteristic of both countries is that they developed
and expanded by means of multinational treaties.
Tell us what will be on the test, already!
What do you expect, this school has only been open for three years.
And it would be a total hassle to go back to Earth.
Hey this school is really pretty.
How do I register someone as a Wired friend?
Hey have you heard the story about the legendary shrine?
They say it will make sure your love is reciprocated.
They say the Dorssia Mil-Fed is violating our territorial space again.
They will probably settle with us by paying a fine.
It is more economical than having a military right?
You saying that sums up everything that is wrong with this country.
Are not you ever going to tell Shoko how you feel?
She is going to get snatchet up by somebody else.
Do not come crying to me when she does.
You have been staring at me like a freak.
If it is nothing, then you should not mind me seeing it.
Come on, there is nothing on it!
If you do not give it back you and I are through as friends!
Why were you looking at me?
I was only thinking, She would be beautiful, if she kept quiet...
I just mean, maybe you could keep your mouth shut!
No, that is not right, either.
Inuzuka-senpai, you are always talking about money.
Because I plan to become the richest person in the world someday.
If you are going to dream dream big, huh?
If you do not mind, could we trouble you for directions?
Are you asking her to the dance or something?
I prefer to mind my manners at all times.
We should keep contact with the locals to a minimum.
The sprinklers are spaced one every 13 meters,
but they change to one every 12.5 meters in front of just that structure.
There are 40 desks in each classroom visible through the windows.
However, the structure was built using common layered construction.
From a load-bearing standpoint, there is no room for extra facility personnel.
I must therefore conclude that it is beneath the building.
I have never seen them around before.
You do not have enough passion in you.
You did not go into it intending to win, did you?
No, it is not like that.
I wish we lived in a world where there was not stuff like winning and losing.
We each could have used half the field just fine.
Would you use a knife to cut the yolk of your ham eggs
and the girl you love in half, too?
Happiness cannot be split into halfsies.
What will you do if someone hits you even when you do not want to fight?
If you cannot concede, your only choice is to fight.
Miss Nanami, what are you doing?
I am here to give Rukino extra lessons, but she is not here yet.
I wonder if I told her the wrong time?
List of students signed up for extra lessons.
Sheesh, what was that guy's deal?
Sorry, pal, but I am the kind of girl who eats the egg white first.
And anyway, the star of ham eggs is the ham!
And Haruto was the one who was knocked down, right?
I think that is what happened...
What Haruto said was totally noble!
He was not wrong, so what the hell?
You are getting angry so I do not have to.
That makes me feel a lot better.
Well, that is what friends are for.
I mean, you never get mad at anything.
We were supposed to keep contact to a minimum.
Are you making a wish, too, Haruto?
They say if you profess your feelings here, your feelings are sure to be returned.
Schools that were built three years ago do not have old legends, right?
Bats fly across the cloudy sky.
That is the Colonel's star pupil for you...
Kind of low, are not they?
Dorssian model number NW507Be, manned Waffe units!
Everyone, get inside the school building!
Hostiles confirmed as Dorssia Mil-Fed fleet!
Why would the Dorssian military attack us?
Cannot anyone get through to the homeland?
They say they are being blown out of the sky.
Are you going to take responsibility for it?
Aw, he hogged all the fun again!
There is someone inside that car!
This is no time to be playing hide-and-seek!
You just have to accept it!
Let us just sit tight until some adults arrive!
It is not safe here, run!
It is the primary strategic objective!
I will drag out just the pilot.
I will just need a second.
You are a robot, are not you?!
Reports on the, sneak attack against JIOR by the Dorssian army are still spotty.
The government is struggling to respond.
Do not you have any weapons?
Come on, you are a weapon, are not you?
You did not go into it intending to win, did you?
If you cannot concede, you have to fight.
Its color and power are different, too!
We will not lose to a military that is never known war!
What the hell is that light?!
What kind of light is that?
He is in the class next door.
That is the boy from this morning!
I have seen him before somewhere...
Him and me, we are friends!
That is a kid in there!
They say he is a high-schooler!
Why does he have a robot?
That is the guy who lost this morning!
Just like you said, a world without winners and losers is a fantasy.
Valvrave the Liberator; it is the system to reveal the truth of the world.
